s":[{"id":1985,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/02\/22\/banner-yawm-al-qiyamah\/","url_meta":{"origin":26180,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Treachery: Betrayal exposed to all on Judgment Day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 22, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar\u00a0reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him,\u00a0said, \u201cWhen Allah gathers the earlier and later generations on the Day of Resurrection, He will raise a banner for every treacherous liar. It will be announced that this is the betrayal of this person, the son of this\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15740,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/20\/fear-muslims-kill-for-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":26180,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Greed: The Prophet fears Muslims will fight for wealth","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"'Uqbah ibn 'Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said,\u00a0\"Verily, I am not afraid that you will commit idolatry, rather I am afraid you will compete with each other for the world.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 4042, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2296 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11839,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/25\/permission-to-keep-gifts\/","url_meta":{"origin":26180,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Gifts: Take gifts to keep or give away in charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, gave me a gift and I said, \"Give it to someone poorer than me.\" The Prophet said, \"Take it and keep it or give it in charity. Whatever comes to you of this property, take it without extravagance\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":617,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/03\/11\/signs-hour-sin-fitnah-murder\/","url_meta":{"origin":26180,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Fitnah: Killing, upheaval, sin before the Hour","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 11, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Time will pass rapidly, knowledge will be withdrawn, tribulations will prevail, greed will be cast into hearts, and there will be many upheavals.\u201d They said, \"What is upheaval?\" The Prophet said, \"It is killing.\" Source: \u1e62a\u1e25\u012b\u1e25 al-Bukh\u0101r\u012b 7061,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":799,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/05\/21\/valley-gold-still-wants-more\/","url_meta":{"origin":26180,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Greed: If he had all the gold, he still wants more","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 21, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas bin Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"If the son of Adam had a valley full of gold, he would want to have two valleys. Nothing fills his mouth but the dust of the grave, yet Allah will relent to whoever repents\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15753,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/20\/honest-business-barakah\/","url_meta":{"origin":26180,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Trade: Honest business is blessed, lying is not","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Hakim ibn Hizam reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBoth parties in a business transaction have the right to annul it, as long as they have not separated. If they are truthful and clear with one another, their transaction is blessed. If they lie and conceal\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/26180","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":